Output Valid CFB Team Names and Abbreviations

Source: R/utils.R
valid_team_names.Rd

Output Valid CFB Team Names and Abbreviations

Usage

valid_team_names(
  division = c("FBS", "P5", "G5", "FCS", "DII", "DIII", "Conference", "hoopR", "Other")
)

Arguments

division

Division to filter for. Options include:

  • FBS

  • P5

  • G5

  • FCS

  • DII

  • DIII

  • Conference

  • hoopR

  • Other

Examples

# List valid team abbreviations excluding duplicates
cfbplotR::valid_team_names("FBS")
